title: Banksy protests imprisonment of Turkish artist
text:
Banksy protests imprisonment of Turkish artist 12:33am IST - 00:47 
Anonymous street artist Banksy has created two new works in New York, one of which depicts detained Turkish artist Zehra Dogan. Jayson Mansaray reports. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
